@fkiraly about the two open checkboxes:
There is already an issue opened for GPU functionality, which is in progress: https://github.com/alan-turing-institute/sktime/issues/3020
Issue with the first checkbox (related to `convert_y_to_keras` was related to where should we move it. If we do decide to have a common DL class as discussed here: https://github.com/alan-turing-institute/sktime/issues/3190 we can simply move it there. Otherwise we might need to create a utils file for it.
